	* common/iobuf.h (IOBUFCTRL_DESC): Change the call semantics.
	* common/iobuf.c (iobuf_desc): Add the second argument DESC.
	(print_chain, iobuf_close, do_open, iobuf_sockopen, iobuf_ioctl)
