2015-10-05  Werner Koch  <wk@gnupg.org>

	gpg: Install a dirmngr.conf file.
	* g10/dirmngr-conf.skel: New.
	* g10/Makefile.am (EXTRA_DIST): Add file.
	(install-data-local, uninstall-local): Install that file.
