	* g10/options.skel: Remove --keyserver entry.

	gpg: Deprecate the --keyserver option.
	* g10/keyserver.c (keyserver_refresh): Change return type to
	gpg_error_t.  Use gpg_dirmngr_ks_list to print the name of the
	keyserver to use.
