	(ks_action_help): If the provided URI is an LDAP URI, then use
	ldap_parse_uri to parse.  Call ks_ldap_help.
	(ks_action_search): If passed an LDAP URI, then call ks_ldap_search.
	(ks_action_get): Likewise.
