	* g10/sig-check.c (do_check): Move some code to ...
	* g10/misc.c (print_md5_rejected_note): new function.
	* g10/mainproc.c (proc_tree, proc_plaintext): Enable MD5 workaround
	only if option --allow-weak-digest-algos is used.

