	* sm/server.c (gpgsm_server): Ditto.
	* dirmngr/dirmngr-client.c (start_dirmngr): Likewise.
	* tools/gpgconf.c (main): Print "dirmngr-sys-socket" with --list-dirs.

	* configure.ac (USE_DIRMNGR_AUTO_START): Set by default.

